    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/402a48b2caa393fc7198996d264fdf7d.poster.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/402a48b2caa393fc7198996d264fdf7d.webm?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/402a48b2caa393fc7198996d264fdf7d.mp4?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Age of Respair 是一款中世纪城堡建设主题策略游戏。您将在游戏中管理王国的方方面面：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>收集资源并建立生产链条。<br></li><li>实现人口增长以扩大城堡和经济规模。 <br></li><li>加强防御以抵御连续不断的无情围攻。<br></li><li>组建庞大的军队以攻打敌人的城堡。</li></ul><br>您可完成由故事线驱动的战役，或与 AI 对手展开激烈战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/ed769d46424dde5c18a3c3c4d94e4a11.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/23ce184a0eaae55114ee50af1a54b300.poster.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/23ce184a0eaae55114ee50af1a54b300.webm?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/23ce184a0eaae55114ee50af1a54b300.mp4?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收集木材、石头和铁等必要资源。工人收集这些资源并运送到仓库后，就可将其在生产链中投入使用。不要忘了为人民提供食物 — 可以选择快捷方式，比如苹果园；也可以建立更强大的食物系统，比如可以为为磨坊和面包房提供原料的麦田。王国的繁荣复兴取决于您的每一个决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/68c6c28e7a8620d6e0f712bd505fc0fe.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/8e093829489f72fcf56f3da6964469e6.poster.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/8e093829489f72fcf56f3da6964469e6.webm?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/8e093829489f72fcf56f3da6964469e6.mp4?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>管理人民的幸福感对保持王国繁荣复兴至关重要。如果您的人民不快乐，他们可能会离开工作岗位，甚至离开城堡。您可以建造教堂、酒馆和其他娱乐设施来鼓舞士气。<br>另外，您也可以通过设置刑具等恐吓物来进行恐惧统治，以牺牲幸福感为代价提高生产力。<br>您需要明智地平衡自己的声誉：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>幸福的公民会缴纳更多的税收。<br></li><li>恐惧可以提高资源产量。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/c9c87496ca47dfa966adf0a0f8b5c6e6.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/7ad8e73441fe7ebb6b3570389d779538.poster.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/7ad8e73441fe7ebb6b3570389d779538.webm?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/7ad8e73441fe7ebb6b3570389d779538.mp4?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着王国的发展，王国内部的需求也会增加。您可以从最基础的建筑开始升级以提高效率、确保经济发展与您的宏图伟略统一步调。战略性升级是保持经济繁荣强大的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/abbf64fc4c22dd9759177253495b194f.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/34cb4ce3b3c511ccba8bb2d486b49e6b.poster.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/34cb4ce3b3c511ccba8bb2d486b49e6b.webm?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/34cb4ce3b3c511ccba8bb2d486b49e6b.mp4?t=1762364349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>您可以用坚固的城墙、战略塔楼和护城河加强防御，保护您的王国不受敌人入侵。您需要不惜一切代价保护国王。<br>一旦王国的防守稳固了，就要将重点集中在进攻上。生产武器、训练士兵并使用攻城武器（如弩炮、弹射器和攻城塔）攻克敌人的城堡。由于战争迷雾系统会隐藏敌人的位置，细致的侦查和战略规划将是获胜的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164360/extras/aaf9e4864a34ac3562d4329a8a29159f.avif?t=1762364349\" width=616 height=90 /></span><br>您可以加入我们的 Discord反馈社区，与我们交流、分享您的想法，并率先参与 alpha 和 beta 测试阶段的游戏。快来帮助我们塑造游戏，与其他爱好者交流，共同打造令人惊叹的游戏吧！",
